OL,3,CFarm animals were so malnourished they
OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FA father and daughter subjected
OL,7,Fanimals at their farm in Pembrokeshire
OL,8,Fto unnecessarily poor and unsafe
OL,9,Fliving conditions, a court has heard.
OL,11,FRichard Scarfe, 44, and his 26-year-
OL,12,Fold daughter Brogan Scarfe were
OL,13,Fsentenced at Swansea Crown Court on
OL,14,FMonday after officers from
OL,15,FPembrokeshire County Council found
OL,16,Fevidence of animals including pigs,
OL,17,Fsheep, dogs, and poultry suffering
OL,18,Fneedlessly in 'appalling living
OL,19,Fconditions' and without a regular
OL,20,Fsource of food or water.
