OL,3,CFarm animals were so malnourished they
OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FBut over the course of numerous
OL,7,Funannounced visits the council found
OL,8,Fthe father-of-three was routinely
OL,9,Fcarrying out husbandry activities at
OL,10,Fthe farm while dead pigs were
OL,11,Fdiscovered next to living pigs.
OL,13,FFootage played in court by the
OL,14,Fprosecution also showed pigs screaming
OL,15,Fin pain while stuck in extremely
OL,16,Fcramped spaces. The court heard pigs
OL,17,Fwere so inappropriately housed in
OL,18,Flarge numbers that it resulted in
OL,19,Ffighting, aggression, and injury.
