OL,3,CFarm animals were so malnourished they
OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FThe council found one pig was missing
OL,7,Fpart of its ear which had clearly been
OL,8,Fchewed off. According to experts
OL,9,Fcommissioned by the council this was
OL,10,Flikely as a result of cannibalistic
OL,11,Fbehaviour caused by the pigs at the
OL,12,Ffarm competing for the limited food
OL,13,Fand space while sheep were also
OL,14,Fphotographed very malnourished.
