OL,3,CFarm animals were so malnourished they
OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FMr Jowett explained during numerous
OL,7,Fvisits it was discovered that animals
OL,8,Fat the site were not being regularly
OL,9,Ffed or offered clean drinking water.
OL,10,FOften there was no food or water
OL,11,Favailable to pigs and sheep at all.
OL,12,FVeterinary surgeons from the Animal
OL,13,Fand Plant Health Agency were asked by
OL,14,Fthe council to assist and to provide
OL,15,Findependent veterinary opinion on
OL,16,Fcattle, pigs, sheep, and poultry.
