OL,3,CFarm animals were so malnourished they
OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FThe court heard Richard Scarfe ignored
OL,7,Fthe veterinary opinions that the
OL,8,Fanimals on the site were suffering
OL,9,Funnecessarily as a result of serious
OL,10,Ffailures in their care. Veterinary
OL,11,Fofficers then issued a certificate
OL,12,Funder section 18 of the Animal Welfare
OL,13,FAct 2006 for the removal of the
OL,14,Fanimals to a place of safety and to
OL,15,Fprevent further suffering.
