OL,3,CFarm animals were so malnourished they
OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FDuring the final visits to the farm in
OL,7,FApril 2023 one cow, 26 sheep, 43 pigs,
OL,8,F23 poultry, and five dogs were seized
OL,9,Fand removed to a place of sanctuary
OL,10,Fwhere they were examined by a
OL,11,Fveterinary surgeon with many needing
OL,12,Fmedical intervention.
OL,14,FThe court heard Richard Scarfe, of
OL,15,FPark Street, Pembroke Dock, pleaded
OL,16,Fguilty to two offences of causing
OL,17,Funnecessary suffering to a protected
OL,18,Fanimal, namely pigs and sheep, on the
OL,19,Fsecond day of a trial.
