OL,4,Cstarted trying to eat each other
OL,6,FBrogan Scarfe, of Woodbine Terrace,
OL,7,FPembroke, also pleaded guilty to two
OL,8,Foffences of failing in her duty to
OL,9,Ftake reasonable steps in all the
OL,10,Fcircumstances to ensure that the needs
OL,11,Fof an animal, namely sheep and pigs,
OL,12,Ffor which they are responsible are met
OL,13,Fto the extent required by good
OL,14,Fpractice. She also pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Fthe charges on the second day of her
OL,16,Ftrial.
