OL,6,FJudge Richards gave Richard Scarfe a
OL,7,Flifetime ban preventing him from ever
OL,8,Fkeeping animals again. He was
OL,9,Fsentenced to 11 months in prison
OL,10,Fsuspended for 12 months and was
OL,11,Fordered to complete 200 hours of
OL,12,Funpaid work, a 12-month mental health
OL,13,Ftreatment requirement, and 15 days of
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity.
OL,16,FJudge Richards gave Brogan Scarfe a 12-
OL,17,Fmonth community order comprising 100
OL,18,Fhours of unpaid work. She was
OL,19,Fdisqualified from keeping animals for
OL,20,Ffive years.
